{"tid":2114832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★據報英國希望讓日本電氣和富士通 參與建設當地5G網絡 取代華為","createTime":"2020-07-19T06:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T12:30:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"97fa24499d0aa0cd7ffdf5bbb8d845ac83814099","tid":2114832,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"《日本經濟新聞》報道，英方官員上周四，與日本國家安全保障局等機構的官員會面，尋求在5G技術方面合作，<strong>希望讓日本電氣和富士通兩間企業向英國供應5G網絡零件</strong>。日方亦同意在發展5G技術上，需要跟英國企業合作。<br />\n<br />\n英國電訊網絡供應一直以諾基亞和愛立信為主，原本引入華為是希望促進競爭，以提升網絡技術及降低成本，現在英國就希望日本企業，能取代華為的角色。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5f13cfd8335d19d95330ba83/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%97%A5%E4%BC%81%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B05G%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1-%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5f13cfd8335d19d95330ba83%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258B%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B05G%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1-%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=d6b29e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5f13cfd8335d19d95330ba83/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%97%A5%E4%BC%81%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B05G%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1-%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA</a>"},{"pid":"56afeb01107f110174fb10178e54baee156d13c5","tid":2114832,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im